        walkthrough = '1. Note that you do not specifically need to be allied to Bastok to start this quest.\n2. Exit Bastok Markets (S) into North Gustaberg (S) at (G-4). Upon exiting, a cutscene will play where you obtain the [Key Item]Clump of animal hair.\n3. Take the key item to Engelhart at the Music Shop in Bastok Markets (S) at (K-10).\n4. Head out to the waterfall in North Gustaberg (S) at (F-8).\n   - This is near the survival guide.\n   - Examine the ??? on the right side of the waterfall.\n5. You will be asked to retrieve an item from a Goblin NPC in Vunkerl Inlet (S).\n6. Buy a Gnole Claw from Auction House (Materials ➞ Bonecraft) to make the next step quicker.\n7. Head to Vunkerl Inlet (S) to find the goblin Leadavox at (J-6) and trade him a Gnole Claw for [Key Item]Xhifhut.\n   - Gnoles can be found at (E-7) in Vunkerl Inlet (S).\n   - Decrepit Gnoles can be found at (H-11) in Jugner Forest (S).\n8. Afterwards, head back to Bastok Markets (S) and speak to Engelhart to complete the quest.',
        notes = nil,
    },
