        description = 'Mission Orders: Could it be that the Walk of Echoes holds the key to the enigma that is the Voidwalker menace? With no word from Cait Sith or the mysterious moogle Kupofried, you decide to head to the Pashhow Marshlands rendezvous point to investigate...',
