        fame_level = nil,
        title = 'Assistant Detective',
        repeatable = 'No',
        previous = {'Light in the Darkness'},
        next = {'Storm on the Horizon'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Gentle Tiger (S) in Bastok Markets (S) at (H-6) for a cutscene that begins the quest.\n2. Speak to Engelhart in Bastok Markets (S) at (K-10).\n3. From Batallia Downs (S), use the (J-10) entrance to The Eldieme Necropolis (S).\n   - The quickest way is via Survival Guide to The Eldieme Necropolis (S).\n   - Alternatively: via Voidwatch teleport (Jeuno I)\n4. Go to the southern room at (G-9) and fall down the center hole. Follow the path, then make a left turn at the fork and go up the stairs. At the top, enter the room to the north at (I-7). Check the Sarcophagus on the east side of the room for a cutscene.\n   - There are four Orcs in this room, so either clear them out before you watch the cutscene or wait for them to turn to drop invisible.\n5. Speak to Gentle Tiger (S) for a cutscene.\n6. Speak to Blatherix at (F-8) for your reward.\n   - You should keep this Elixir for use in a later mission, The Truth Lies Hid.\nIf you are working on missions then return to Cait Sith (Mission).',
        notes = nil,
