        next = {'Claws of the Griffon'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Note that you do not specifically need to be allied to San d\'Oria to start this quest.\n2. You must talk to to Louxiard in Southern San d\'Oria (S) at G-7 and watch the cutscene.\n3. Leave the area then return to Louxiard for another cutscene.\n   - Using Retrace counts as zoning here, and you can quickly resume your progress.\n4. Talk to Rholont at E-7 to begin the actual quest. A cutscene will play that lists people you need to trade the Plumes d\'Or to:\n   - Machionage (C-6)\n   - Louxiard (G-7)\n   - Illeuse (H-9)\n   - Rongelouts N Distaud (I-9)\n   - Sabiliont (by the chocobo stable at I-11)\n   - Elnonde (K-9)\n   - Loillie (she\'s up on a ledge at K-9 but you\'ll have to go up the stairs at L-8 to reach her)\n5. Return to Rholont to finish the quest and receive the reward.',
