        start_npc = 'Halver',
        start_zone = 'Chateau d\'Oraguille',
        start_pos = 'I-9',
        description = 'Despite no longer having memories of Lilisette, Halver\'s words spoken from his subconscious suggest that not all is lost. Could the Larzos of your reality possess knowledge that would aid your cause? Make haste to where he and you first met, at Sir Ragelise\'s gravestone.',
