        walkthrough = '1. Speak with Hampu-Kampu located in the south map of Windurst Waters (S) (G-8).\n   - He is standing right outside the gate currently blocking entrance to Gingerberry Grove and rest of southwest Windurst Waters (S).\n2. Interact with the Door: Acolyte hostel located in the north map at (K-4).\n   - Second floor, on the right side of the left building.\n3. Return to Hampu-Kampu for another cutscene, and to receive the [Key Item] Torn patches of leather.\n4. Speak with Kipopo in Southern San d\'Oria (present) at (D-8).\n   - She is inside the room on the first floor.\n5. Trade her a Laminated Ram Leather, Sheep Leather and Silk Thread.\n6. Zone, then speak with her again. You will receive the [Key Item] Repaired handbag.\n7. Return to Hampu-Kampu to finish the quest and receive the Trainee\'s Needle.',
