        previous = {'Father and Son'},
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Exoroche (S) at Southern San d\'Oria (S) (K-9) for a cutscene that begins the quest.\n   - (Optional) Speak to Exoroche in Southern San d\'Oria (K-7).\n   - (Optional) Speak to Ailbeche in Northern San d\'Oria (J-9).\n2. Speak to Landeric in Jugner Forest (S) (G-5).\n   - Zone into Jugner Forest (S) from East Ronfaure (S), using the Survival Guide for the fastest route.\n3. Speak to Exoroche (S) at Southern San d\'Oria (S) (K-9) to receive a Bronze Sword.\n4. Trade the Bronze Sword to Exoroche (S) (K-9) for a brief cutscene. He will return it to you.\n5. Trade the Bronze Sword to Landeric in Jugner Forest (S) (G-5) for a brief cutscene.\n   - You will be given multiple options. If you chose the wrong ones the sword will be returned to you.\n   - The proper answers seem to be:\n     - "Ask about Exoroche."\n     - "Not in the slightest!"\n     - "The boy\'s spirit is true."\n     - "Protect his family and kingdom."\n6. Speak to Exoroche (S) at Southern San d\'Oria (S) (K-9) to receive Trainee\'s Spectacles.\n7. If you speak to Exoroche in Southern San d\'Oria (K-7) with the Trainee\'s Spectacles equipped, you will see a brief extra cutscene.',
