        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Begin quest by speaking with Naiko-Paneiko, just inside the entrance of Crawlers\' Nest (S) at (L-8) (when you enter from Rolanberry Fields (S)). He will give you a [Key Item] Scoop-Dedicated Linkpearl.\n2. Go to (G-9) in Rolanberry Fields (S) and talk to Rakula-Motakula, who is upon a ballista up the hill, behind the long fence.\n3. When prompted, talk about the Mandragoras.\n4. He will ask you 3 questions, how many leafed mandies there are, then how many black mandies, and finally how many flowered mandies there are. The answer is  4, 4, and 5.\n5. Head back to Naiko-Paneiko for your reward.',
